Surf_trance_v1

This is a linear, surf, style map with a jail.  Map was tested on 32 man 100 tic servers with no lag over a period of two months.  Surf settings of; sv_accelerate 10 and sv_airaccelerate 100 were used.   As always, any problems, please let me know.

Thank you, and enjoy,

 UZY
